ound the website. These cookies do not collect data that could identify you and are only used to help us improve our website and how it works. They also help us understand our users' interests and measure our effectiveness.\"},\"functional\":{\"title\":\"Functional cookies\",\"description\":\"These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalization, improving your visit. They may be set by us or by a third party whose services we have added to our pages. They are used to remember your settings and whether we have already asked if you have read and understood our cookies notice. If you do not allow these cookies, then some or all of these services may not function properly.\"},\"targeting\":{\"title\":\"Targeting cookies\",\"description\":\"These cookies are linked to services provided by us and/or third parties and may be set through our website by us and/or our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant advertisements on our website and other websites. They may also be used for other advertising purposes including serving and rendering advertisements, frequency capping, tracking clicks, personalizing advertisements and any other research relating to serving advertisements. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. These cookies are not necessary for the function of the website and you can choose to not allow them\"},\"popup\":{\"title\":\"You are in control of cookies used\",\"description\":\"KICK and our partners use cookies to enhance your browsing experience, serve personalized content, measure how the website is used, and for advertising, marketing and social media purposes. By clicking \\\"Accept all\\\", you consent to our use of cookies.\"}},\"accept\":\"Accept\",\"reject\":\"Reject\"},\"CategoryDialog\":{\"title\":\"Update stream category\",\"selected_category\":\"Selected cate